{
  "stem": "1415.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she had like some food in her arm, like a bag of something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He took the bag, and he threw it, took it out of her hands.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He threw it, and he hit her very strongly with that poke, and he grabbed my arm.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And by that time, the whole group sort of separated, because they were scared to death of him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he threw me against the wall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know how far that wall was, but it was very far away, especially for me, as a kid.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because, the next thing I knew, I must have passed out, because when I-- when I came to, there was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was all by myself with that SS.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] He got me to stand up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he-- and-- and by that time, these Polish kids were standing around and-- and laughing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was asking me whether I knew where people were hidden.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I-- I said, no, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he-- he took me around to a couple places where I know people were there or used to be there, and he couldn't find anybody.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I tried to make a deal with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, look, if you don't find anybody, can I go and see my mother and father the last time?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I knew what he-- he had in mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and those Polish kids were following us around wherever we went.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it seemed like an eternity because we went through that whole place, and in my child's eye, it was a very large place, many buildings, and many places to go and see.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They even took me to that kettle where-- where I sat amongst the pipes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a couple of corpses there inside.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
